item.title: A recipe for success: Reimagining the WildMoose Bakers website
item.description: Learn more about my process creating a new website for WildMoose Bakers, an artisan bakery in Morrisville, NC. From preserving their warm, traditional vibe to crafting a dynamic, mobile-friendly design, this case study delves into the research, design, and development process behind their new digital home.
